Install Instructions For extDB

Server Side and Database:

1. Navigate to Server_Files/@extDB/extdb-conf.ini and edit to your servers database type, port, 
   user name Id and password
2. Copy @extDB folder to the root of your arma server.
3. Add '@extDB' to your servers mod list in your start bat or mod line if using a host.
4. Run the sql query.sql into your servers database.
5. Navigate to your dayz_server/init/server_functions.sqf and find:

onPlayerDisconnected "[_uid,_name] call server_onPlayerDisconnect;";
   
   below that paste:
   
/*extDB*/
 "extDB" callExtension "9:DATABASE:Database2";
 "extDB" callExtension format["9:ADD:DB_RAW_V2:%1",1];
 "extDB" callExtension "9:LOCK";

extDB install complete, now move on to the Starter Kit.